    { "@type": "Question", name: "How much space do I need for a packing station?", acceptedAnswer: { "@type": "Answer", text: "A single-operator packing station needs a minimum 1.5m × 0.8m table plus 0.5m clearance on each side for movement. For high-volume operations, 2m × 1m benches with adjacent storage shelving are ideal. Always ensure clear access to tape dispensers, label printers, and box supply from a standing position." } },
